about.summary: Provides support for non-gregorian datetimes in matplotlib based on the cftime package

name: nc-time-axis
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "1.2.0" %}

package:
  name: nc-time-axis
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://github.com/SciTools/nc-time-axis/archive/v{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 49c4b1022e601e22a2fb5fc6fc2af69070cceb5cdd01a880ae7379caef8f2f90

build:
  number: 0
  noarch: python
  script: python -m pip install --no-deps --ignore-installed .

requirements:
  build:
    - python
    - pip
  run:
    - python
    - cftime
    - matplotlib
    - numpy
    - six

test:
  imports:
    - nc_time_axis

about:
  home: https://github.com/SciTools/nc-time-axis
  license: BSD 3-Clause
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: 'Provides support for non-gregorian datetimes in matplotlib based on the cftime package'

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - lbdreyer
    - ocefpaf
    - pelson
